Saras Says It’s Interested in Investing in Romanian Wind Farms

-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 
2011-06-02T14:35:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/saras-says-it-s-interested-in-investing-in-romanian-wind-farms.html
Saras SpA (SRS) , the owner of the
Mediterranean region’s largest oil refinery, is interested in
investing in wind farms in  Romania , the Balkan nation’s Economy
Ministry said.  The Bucharest-based ministry commented in an e-mailed
statement after a meeting with Saras Chief Executive Officer
Massimo Moratti.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alan Crosby at 
 acrosby1@bloomberg.net  